title: MIP 18: Add mUSD/FEI Feeder Pool
body:
[MIP-18](https://mips.mstable.org/MIPS/mip-18.html) proposes to add an mUSD/FEI Feeder Pool as specified in [MIP 9](https://mips.mstable.org/MIPS/mip-9.html) on Ethereum mainnet. FEI is an algorithmic stablecoin that is collateralized by PCV (Protocol Controlled Value) and is fully decentralised.

**Should we move forward and create a proposal as PDP-34?**
author: 0xE76Be9C1e10910d6Bc6b63D8031729747910c2f6
